{"tid":422171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（秋後算賬）西班牙：有權中止加泰隆尼亞自治權","createTime":"2017-10-02T23:12:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-03T00:01:11.000Z","uid":41351,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22d44f1af59d6250fad8adb489d75e169444fe4f","tid":422171,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"加泰隆尼亞自治區昨天舉行獨立公投。AP<br />\n1/1加泰隆尼亞自治區昨天舉行獨立公投。AP<br />\n西班牙加泰隆尼亞自治區昨天舉行獨立公投，西班牙司法部長卡塔拉（Rafael Catala）表示，假如加泰隆尼亞議會宣布獨立，西班牙可動用憲法權力中止這個地區的自治權。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，根據西班牙憲法第155條，中央政府可中止這個東北部地區的自治權。卡塔拉接受電視台訪問時表示，憲法第155條列明西班牙可將動用完整的法律效力。並指政府的責任是解決問題，即使採取若干行動可能造成傷害。但倘有人宣布獨立，政府就必須告訴他們不得如此。<br />\n----<br />\n大家後面了就不會留手"},{"pid":"cc9c34f140efbfbf0f8d95968c181c3adc9676b7","tid":422171,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:14:51.000Z","msg":"補link<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1028090/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1028090%2F&d=CmemZmFyzWbYnZ7Ld0a%2FVnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=577925eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1028090%2F&h=1e44271d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1028090/</a>"},{"pid":"f3831221d0a1277b9d13ed260151ae30de07c36d","tid":422171,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:28:28.000Z","msg":"一宣佈獨立<br />\n仲洗鬼要你賜予自治權？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acc91193c4bd54cee12e3b850b30ab818e9b406","tid":422171,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:46:32.000Z","msg":"牙你老母"},{"pid":"3f8e2ac588e42d1bfe2eb1e38e06344400909bc9","tid":422171,"uid":71315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T23:59:16.000Z","msg":"千其唔好用暴力，和平係我地最大既武器<br />\n要用愛與和平穿透警方防線<br />\n千其唔好激嬲西班牙政府<br />\n要爭取國際聲音既支持<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8865e109a9f7f0e9845d354e64f040427cb73cdc","tid":422171,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T00:01:11.000Z","msg":"自治政府自行組織警察同軍隊唔得？"}]}